<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.6">
<l>kārttaṇ mukiluṅ karuviḷaiyuṅ kāyā malaruṅ kamalappūvum</l>
<l>īrttiṭu kiṉṟaṉa veṉṉaivantiṭ ṭiruṭīkē caṉpakkal pōkēyeṉṟu</l>
<l>vērttup pacittu vayiṟacaintu vēṇṭaṭici luṇṇum pōtīteṉṟu</l>
<l>pārttiruntu neṭunōkkuk koḷḷum pattavi lōcanat tuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cool black clouds, mussel-shell creepers, ironwood flowers, and lotuses</l>
<l>Come [before me] and are pulling me saying, “Go to Hṛṣīkeśa!”</l>
<l>Send [me] to Bhaktavilocana where [He] gives a long glance</l>
<l>Waiting [for the ascetics’s wives] thinking, “This is the time to eat the required rice!’</l>
<l rend="indent">After sweating, feeling hunger, and the belly stirred [in hunger].’</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
